szakacs.kpi.fei.tuke.intrfc.arena.game.world

Interface HorizontalTunnelBasic

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    HorizontalTunnelUpdatable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HorizontalTunnel

    public interface HorizontalTunnelBasic

    The base interface for a class representing a tunnel stretching from left to right on the screen.

    This is the interface of such a class that is exposed to the player.
